</head>
<body>

  <div id="wrapper">
    <div id="main" class="clearfix">
      <div id="logo"></div>

      <%= yield %>

      <div id="help">
        <p>
          When you run a promo in Twitter you should use some hashtag like #mypromo to track what users
          participate. You will also need a way to find the winner between all the tweets with the hash
          #mypromo. How you will do that?</p>
        <p>Just place you promo hashtag in the field above to find the lucky guy.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="footer">
    <div class="left txt_right">
      <p>Design &amp; development <a href="http://twitter.com/danielvlopes">Daniel Lopes</a></p>
      <p>Bird illustration by
      <a href="http://freakyframes.deviantart.com/">=freakyframes</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="area left">
      <img src="images/area.png"/>
    </div>
  </div>

